title: Disney Pixar's "A Bug's Life" - Hebrew dubbing
description:
This is a torrent the includes the Hebrew dubbed version of "A Bug's Life", the 1998 Pixar animated film about an ant named Flik that goes out to the big city to recruit a group of bug soldiers, which will help him to beat the grasshopper-bullies that attack his colony once a year.

Dubbing actors list:

- Flik: Tomer Sharon
- Atta: Sharon Shahal
- Dot: Shirley Wertheimer 
- The Queen: Tiki Dayan 
- Francis: Alon Ofir
- Heimlich: Chen Alon
- Salim: Yossi Toledo
- Rosie: Rama Mesinger 
- Manny: Yehuda Efroni
- Gypsy: Lilian Berto
- Tuck & Roll: Dor Zweigenboim
- Dim: Gil Zemek
- P.T. Flea: Eyal Bertonov
- Hopper: Yuval Zamir
- Molt: Efron Etkin
- Mr. Soil: Dov Raizer
- Dr. Flora: Shaphrira Zakay
- Cornelius: Shmulik Tene
